JMS `Topic`s should be replaced with MicroProfile `Emitter`s feeding a Channel. See the following example of migrating
 a Topic to an Emitter:

 Before:
 ```
 @Resource(lookup = "java:/topic/HELLOWORLDMDBTopic")
 private Topic topic;
 ```

 After:
 ```
 @Inject
 @Channel("HELLOWORLDMDBTopic")
 Emitter<String> topicEmitter;
 ```

